dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Frazier Mountain & Lebec quadrangles, Los Angeles, Ventura & Kern Counties, California
dct_alternative_sm: Geology Frazier Mountain and Lebec quadrangles
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
Contour interval: Frazier Mountain quadrangle 50 feet ; Lebec quadrangle 40 feet.
"Topographic base map from newest available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle, Frazier Mountain, CA 1958, AMS 2253 IV SW-Series V895; Lebec, CA 1995, NIMA 2253 IV SE-Series V895."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
